fields.name: Patterned chiffon blouse
fields.description: Oversized blouse in sheer chiffon with an all-over pattern. Band collar with gathers all around and a V-shaped opening at the front. Long balloon sleeves with narrow, buttoned cuffs and a gathered seam at the front of the waist for added volume.

fields.name: V-neck blouse
fields.description: V-neck blouse in woven fabric with a sheen. Collar, buttons down the front, long sleeves with a sleeve placket and buttoned cuffs, and a rounded hem.

fields.name: Oversized linen shirt
fields.description:
Premium Selection
Oversized shirt in airy linen with a collar, buttons down the front and an open chest pocket. Yoke at the back, gently dropped shoulders, long sleeves with adjustable buttoning at the cuffs and a sleeve placket with a link button. Straight-cut hem with curved side vents.

fields.name: Linen-blend shirt
fields.description: Shirt in an airy weave made from a linen and viscose blend. Collar, buttons down the front, an open chest pocket and a double-layered yoke with a box pleat at the back. Long sleeves with buttoned cuffs. Rounded hem.

fields.name: MAMA Before & After Linen-blend shirt
fields.description: Shirt in an airy weave made from a linen blend. Collar, buttons down the front and a double-layered yoke at the back. Gently dropped shoulders and long sleeves with buttoned cuffs. Narrow, detachable tie belt below the bust and a straight-cut hem with curved side vents. The shirt can be worn both during and after pregnancy.

fields.name: Oversized denim shirt
fields.description: Oversized shirt in supersoft and feather-light denim with a collar, buttons down the front and a yoke at the back. Dropped shoulders and long sleeves with a sleeve placket and buttoned cuffs. Rounded hem.

fields.name: Denim shirt
fields.description:
New Arrival
Loose-fit shirt in cotton denim with a button-down collar and buttons down the front. Yoke at the back with a box pleat, forward-facing shoulder seams and long sleeves featuring buttoned cuffs and a sleeve placket with a link button. Finished with a rounded hem.

fields.name: Oversized cotton poplin shirt
fields.description: Oversized shirt in crisp cotton poplin with a collar, buttons down the front and an open chest pocket. Yoke at the back, dropped shoulders and long sleeves with buttoned cuffs and a sleeve placket with a link button. Straight-cut hem with curved side vents.

fields.name: Tailored trousers
fields.description: Tailored trousers in woven fabric featuring a high waist with a zip fly and a concealed button and hook-and-bar fasteners. Diagonal side pockets and straight legs with creases down the front and back.

fields.name: Wide joggers
fields.description: Loose-fit joggers in sweatshirt fabric with an elasticated, drawstring waist, discreet pockets in the side seams and wide legs.

fields.name: Canvas cargo trousers
fields.description: Trousers in cotton canvas featuring a low waist with covered elastication at the back and a zip fly and press-stud. Diagonal side pockets and wide legs that have bellows pockets with a flap.

fields.name: Capri trousers
fields.description: 3/4-length trousers in washed cotton twill. Low waist with a diagonal zip fly and carabiner hook fastening. Waistband with wide belt loops, with a metal D-ring on the front belt loop. Diagonal side pockets, flap back pockets and flap leg pockets positioned at different heights. Concealed mini pocket in one of the front seams. Straight legs featuring an elastic drawstring with a cord stopper above the hems and a metal button with a buttonhole at the front and back for various styling options.

fields.name: Sports leggings with SoftMove�
fields.description: Sports leggings in functional fabric made with SoftMove�, which provides the ultimate in softness and comfort plus contouring support, and DryMove�, which helps pull moisture away from your skin. High waist with a wide waist panel.

fields.name: Flared High Jeans
fields.description: Jeans in slightly stretchy denim with a high waist, zip fly and button and legs with wide, flared hems. Fake front pockets and real pockets at the back.

fields.name: Baggy High Jeans
fields.description: 5-pocket jeans in rigid denim that feels firm at first but then softens and loosens with wear. Straight leg with a loose fit from the waist to the hip and a baggy fit from the thigh to the hem. High waist with a zip fly and button. Longer length, designed to fall over the foot with a stacking effect. A design that goes from sleek and chic to sporty and cool.

fields.name: 5-pack pull-on shorts
fields.description: Knee-length shorts in soft cotton jersey. Easy pull-on waist with covered elastication and a drawstring.

fields.name: Curvy Fit Wide Ultra High Jeans
fields.description: Curvy-fit, 5-pocket jeans in rigid cotton denim designed for less gaping at the waist and more room through the hip and thigh. Wide leg with a straight, wide cut from the thigh to the hem. Extra-high waist with a zip fly and button. Regular length, designed to hit the top of the foot with little or no stacking. A denim statement that goes the distance.

fields.name: Skinny High Jeans
fields.description: 5-pocket jeans in stretch denim with a skinny fit from the waist to the hem. High waist with a zip fly and button.

fields.name: Denim jacket
fields.description: Jacket in rigid cotton denim with a collar, zip down the front and a yoke at the back. Long sleeves with buttoned cuffs, flap front pockets and a patch inner pocket on the chest. Adjustable tabs with buttons at the back of the hem.

fields.name: Aviator jacket
fields.description: Short jacket in coated fabric featuring a collar with ribbed jersey lining. Zip down the front, shaping seams at the front and back and an inverted box pleat at the back for added width. Patch front pockets with a flap and an additional welt pocket on top. Dropped shoulders, long sleeves and a tab with a press-stud at the cuffs. Lined.

fields.name: Trench coat
fields.description:
Knee-length, double-breasted trench coat in twill with a collar, hook-and-eye fastener and buttoned storm flap at the front. Loose yoke at the back, welt side pockets, tie belt at the waist and raglan sleeves with a tab and button at the cuffs. Lined.
